title: The Proposal  (MKV)
description:
PG-13 | 1h 48min | Comedy, Drama, Romance | June 19th 2009





A pushy boss forces her young assistant to marry her in order to keep her visa status in the U.S. and avoid deportation to Canada.




Director: Anne Fletcher

Writer: Peter Chiarelli

Stars: Sandra Bullock, Ryan Reynolds, Mary Steenburgen




Feature Commentary with Anne Fletcher and Peter Chiarelli

English, French and Spanish Audio and Subtitles
